title: Mugdha Godse-Rahul Dev in Power Couple
text:
Mugdha Godse-Rahul Dev After admitting to being in a relationship, Mugdha Godse and Rahul Dev seem to be now be coming out in the open. Sources say that the duo have agreed to be a part of the upcoming reality show Power Couple. For the longest time, the duo had kept their relationship under wraps.
But recently, after sharing a picture of her and Rahul relaxing by a pool, on a social networking site, Mugdha confirmed dating Rahul.
In an interview she was Quote: d saying that they were more than friends and that the "feeling is very special". The duo met at a fashion show over a year ago and became close friends.
